    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are assessed; most achieved levels are at or one gradation below required levels, which the team judged acceptable given the Monte Carlo UQ coverage and independent PIV validation dataset. The equivalency of input parameters factor was not formally assessed on the basis that boundary conditions are shared between the computational and experimental protocols, but this rationale does not constitute a formal equivalency demonstration. The package is accepted with the acknowledgement that the unassessed factor represents a residual epistemic gap.",
